{"tid":1102941,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"香港平均房價達970萬冠全球！　分析指租樓月均2.2萬元","createTime":"2019-04-12T05:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T06:01:52.000Z","uid":39027,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d320277ad472e094058a745f20395cbad459b4fe","tid":1102941,"uid":39027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:31:38.000Z","msg":"香港樓價高企，廣大市民要上車可謂日益艱難。近日一份國際調查報告指出，香港平均房價高達124萬美元（約973萬港元），平均豪宅價格則為690萬美元（5,416.5萬港元），成為全球之冠！<br />\n<br />\n世邦魏理仕最新的全球生活報告顯示，平均呎價為2,091美元（約1.64萬港元），平均豪宅呎價為3,436美元（約2.7萬港元），平均月租則為2,777美元（約2.18萬港元）。雖然香港去年建成17,790個私人住宅項目，但由於740萬人口帶來的龐大壓力，加上住宅土地有限，因此仍然不夠滿足住屋需求。<br />\n<br />\n報告分析全球35個主要城市樓價，亞洲樓價仍然高企，平均房價排名第二至五位分別是新加坡、上海、溫哥華及深圳。至於去年名列前茅的大城市，包括紐約、洛杉磯、多倫多、溫哥華、悉尼及墨爾本，則由於樓價升幅放緩，在榜單上的名次下滑，讓位給升幅仍然強勁的歐洲城市。<br />\n<br />\n香港看一場電影平均100元<br />\n<br />\n報告亦分析香港的平均消費數據，買一杯Cappuccino為4.55美元（約35.7港元），看一場電影為12.77美元（約100港元），在非繁忙時間搭一公里的士則是1.09美元（約8.5港元）。另外，電費、水費等每月開支是172美元（約1,350港元），國際學校每年學費則是16,272美元（約12.8萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/317176/%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%88%BF%E5%83%B9%E9%81%94970%E8%90%AC%E5%86%A0%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83-%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%8C%87%E7%A7%9F%E6%A8%93%E6%9C%88%E5%9D%872-2%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F317176%2F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%2596-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%2583%25B9%25E9%2581%2594970%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2586%25A0%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583-%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%259E%2590%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25A7%259F%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%259D%25872-2%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzuaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=9b717d6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/317176/%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%88%BF%E5%83%B9%E9%81%94970%E8%90%AC%E5%86%A0%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83-%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%8C%87%E7%A7%9F%E6%A8%93%E6%9C%88%E5%9D%872-2%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83</a>"},{"pid":"f299c57f5b3bc91b6c79c32b034acc6fef53fc55","tid":1102941,"uid":59492,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:44:04.000Z","msg":"一齊訓街拉"},{"pid":"5f0f92dab5025bf7692a6eb11f865a1b8eb5f5cb","tid":1102941,"uid":228794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港樓世界第一"},{"pid":"610b7cad2d7c2b26e833772a5085daaca9ce2c05","tid":1102941,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:18:07.000Z","msg":"奶波魔呢？重未入嚟嘅"},{"pid":"c6dfdf9a1a519517e4a195ec9f676c5a45e5d103","tid":1102941,"uid":187544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:56:30.000Z","msg":"仲有水位，香港要大幅拋離先得，仲未出現宿舍房，共用廚廁，gogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf043c7ac9f0df327528f4c3ad8f3286c0c65db","tid":1102941,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T09:45:49.000Z","msg":"如果用e個結果既家庭計收入，入息中位數可能去到8萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abd014a2df5f66ab7ada4a7edc19ce05d46d8ae","tid":1102941,"uid":67692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf043c7ac9f0df327528f4c3ad8f3286c0c65db","tid":1102941,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T09:45:49.000Z","msg":"如果用e個結果既家庭計收入，入息中位數可能去到8萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T09:50:31.000Z","msg":"3里， 30年嘅話，大約每月6萬6千HKD 供樓"},{"pid":"91c2d112d1e1d84ad52f7f7681e7ed349a0ae083","tid":1102941,"uid":67692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0abd014a2df5f66ab7ada4a7edc19ce05d46d8ae","tid":1102941,"uid":67